{"tid":1829538,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[舊戲］美劇看中國 美國描繪假想敵 略繪香港 The Last Ship","createTime":"2020-01-18T21:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T15:30:08.000Z","uid":236080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4d8e82a261b4c548c5903a9815a001992d9ec8b6","tid":1829538,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T21:32:48.000Z","msg":"戲名：末日孤艦 The Last Ship<br />\n一共有五季 <br />\n中國作為假想敵在第五季出場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHpQiDD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHpQiDD.jpg&h=2710b340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第一二季劇情簡略背景：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一種人為病毒被意外傳播，Dr Scott 係 名為Nathan James 嘅驅逐艦上研製解藥，並由以Tom Chandler為首嘅團隊保護，過程中與俄羅斯戰艦、英國潛水艇、美國免疫者邪教戰鬥，最終成功製造解藥，並最後解救人民。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2u2RNzs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2u2RNzs.jpg&h=a73cdf03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第三季部分劇情：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n美國發放解藥到亞洲，並希望由中國協助派發，但美國認為中國將解藥自己囤積，並分化假解藥俾其他國家，例如日本，以圖控制亞洲地區並更一度接近與越南爆發戰爭。美國為解放亞洲，以武力快速嘅方法成功逼使中國妥協。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">劇中香港啟德機場：</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AMf0FXQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAMf0FXQ.png&h=2293beb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">劇中駐香港解放軍：</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v4ThJbr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv4ThJbr.png&h=3d5c7d24&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EN2a3bu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEN2a3bu.png&h=d6fb56cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>劇中的中國PRC主席 - 彭主席 President Peng Wu :</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/odGGqqu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FodGGqqu.jpg&h=e0d6cb18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第三季預告：</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NcV275YtQP0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNcV275YtQP0&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1CfW%2F3rzywXjCQwsEwiLy3M%3D&h=c37a5a13\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NcV275YtQP0</a>"},{"pid":"8eba62979acee7abca53b2027f6ac4fd498fa901","tid":1829538,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T21:33:22.000Z","msg":"更正：中國在第三季出場，並非第五季"},{"pid":"e92c2db820b960209e5207a055485cdb0abf7ba5","tid":1829538,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T21:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac96d47fb1cff0b32ca6ede6c4ff6c727c39a72f","tid":1829538,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T00:29:22.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da7ff89441d87e564ead4a5fb4bbb86a7e47424","tid":1829538,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"第二季好正，絕地反cap, DD 鬥sub 仔堅好睇。"},{"pid":"8c2908fcb4d0bfe051c8f936430c3dc5cddf0c14","tid":1829538,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6da7ff89441d87e564ead4a5fb4bbb86a7e47424","tid":1829538,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"第二季好正，絕地反cap, DD 鬥sub 仔堅好睇。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:55:50.000Z","msg":"第五季登陸搶灘！超有電影感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1360dd041fefca3a80687f49f2c3de177453c42f","tid":1829538,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DtKWpn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DtKWpn.jpg&h=a27c226a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白色，是醫護常用顏色。不含任何色素，並容易發現污漬，適用於醫院最應保持潔淨的地方。除此之外，白色還代表純粹的善良和堅定的信念。<br />\n<br />\n當日，醫護們憑藉良心忠實履行自己的使命。今日，政權道德綁架他們這一份熱誠和信念。<br />\n<br />\n他們守護了我們生命和健康，但又誰能守護他們？<br />\n<br />\n全城白絲帶，支持醫護罷工。醫護不是condom，我們與醫護同行。<br />\n<br />\n#全城白絲帶 #撐醫護 #撐罷工 #封關口 #醫護非condom #與醫護同行<br />\n#香港金總 #HKFU #standwithmedics<br />\n<br />\n各位金融人都麻煩幫手填問卷，謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n⚠️⚠️緊急⚠️⚠️<br />\n<br />\n香港金融業職工共同抗疫意見調查<br />\n<br />\n香港金融業職工總會欲以問卷方式詢問同業以工業行動共同抗疫的意願和意見，以制定有效方式向僱主及政府表達對僱員對於安全和健康的憂慮，全民共同抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n由於事態緊急，如策劃任何工業行動必需經過既定程序。故此是次問卷將於1月31日23:59截止。希望同業們積極參與此調查，讓金總能全面理解金融界僱主於防疫措施現況，以及會員和同業於共同抗疫的意願，以制定下一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/toVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FtoVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1CfW%2F3rzywXjCQwsEwiLy3M%3D&h=151552a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/toVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7</a><br />\n<br />\n原post傳送門：<br />\n［行動］［請置頂］全民白絲帶 罷工撐醫護<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848612</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f851c2d8274439a3b6143d24ccadbb0c581621f7","tid":1829538,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c2908fcb4d0bfe051c8f936430c3dc5cddf0c14","tid":1829538,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6da7ff89441d87e564ead4a5fb4bbb86a7e47424","tid":1829538,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"第二季好正，絕地反cap, DD 鬥sub 仔堅好睇。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:55:50.000Z","msg":"第五季登陸搶灘！超有電影感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\